Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.71,0:49:35.85,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,350)\fad(100,100)}请千万不要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.94,0:49:36.29,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fad(100,100)}谢谢你 哥哥
